{"tid":2224106,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱改傳媒定義已溝通 記協：無收通知","createTime":"2020-09-30T09:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T10:02:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4bf75d8f2696060140d66b44102c1d2ce62911","tid":2224106,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:42:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/EOLUENG475FDRKD54RIQH62R7E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FEOLUENG475FDRKD54RIQH62R7E%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kylJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=4878e0db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FEOLUENG475FDRKD54RIQH62R7E%2F&h=69d7c344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/EOLUENG475FDRKD54RIQH62R7E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n稱改傳媒定義已溝通 記協：無收通知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wQesMmeQ7rafbDF8gMDzHhPXlvA=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DGGMUC7LIBBVNKURJLRE5YZAJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwQesMmeQ7rafbDF8gMDzHhPXlvA%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDGGMUC7LIBBVNKURJLRE5YZAJU.jpg&h=9dac0bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■油尖旺區議會多名議員在會議後高舉「五大訴求，缺一不可」手勢。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方早前修訂《警察通例》下「傳媒代表」的定義，.....................................<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警襲孕婦 盲撐下屬  認現場有人叫「大肚婆」PK鄧：嘈雜難聽見<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強昨指出，警方過去拘捕多名宣稱記者的人士。區議員林兆彬關注日後學生媒體和網媒在警方橙帶內採訪會否被捕，並要求交出被捕者中「假記者」數字。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z9sA7pxicsYPUZKJXzOMDjlq-2w=/5760x3840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PTAIQSFONBE5VL7PM25PRMZ5NY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz9sA7pxicsYPUZKJXzOMDjlq-2w%3D%2F5760x3840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPTAIQSFONBE5VL7PM25PRMZ5NY.JPG&h=d1c85ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧炳強<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記協明派三人觀察<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強稱，自己不是專業記者，不能判斷何為專業記者。他聲稱任何人都可以採訪，警方亦可在陽光下執法，不會阻止和騷擾，但前提是不能阻礙警方工作或構成危險，亦需進行採訪工作而非參與活動。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強又重複過往警方的指控，表示在過往的反修例示威中，有身穿黃色反光背心的人涉嫌搶犯及沒有任何記者證等。<br />\n<br />\n記者問他修改《警察通例》「傳媒代表」的定義為何未有諮詢新聞界，鄧炳強稱，通例屬警隊內部指引，因應8月一個行動曾讓部份傳媒進入封鎖區，與部份傳媒和組織討論時知悉有不同意見，警方「因應佢哋嘅意見修改內部指引」，已通知四個主要的記者協會或工會。多次被問到與哪個組織會面，鄧炳強始終未能提供答案，僅稱「好多唔同組織、好多唔同傳媒。」<br />\n<br />\n記協副主席陳朗昇重申，從沒收到警方知會，質疑記協擁有最多會員，但警方卻沒有他們溝通。他認為無事不可對人言，警方應公開與哪個組織會面。他亦擔心，明天民間活動現場，記者採訪可能面對警方阻礙，記協會派出三名觀察員觀察警方應對傳媒的情況。"},{"pid":"f38e4559332f330296c27afbf69d6d15d9f9bf07","tid":2224106,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:49:26.000Z","msg":"記協令人討厭政府 可能已觸犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdd9bc798f3ba0e11c186cd58a34050cfeae305","tid":2224106,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:52:52.000Z","msg":"同大公文匯溝通咗"},{"pid":"7de3260b9c5163a927b7ce530f92ad038637dec5","tid":2224106,"uid":114074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"港共同黑警都唔係第一日扮溝通咗<br />\n之前個travel bubble又扮同澳洲傾咗<br />\n最後人地又否認 <br />\n成日自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}